sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Axon Enterprise Inc (Symbol: AAXN), where a total of 6,155 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 615,500 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 51.8% of AAXN's average daily trading volume over the past month of 1.2 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $32 strike call option expiring January 18, 2019 , with 801 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 80,100 underlying shares of AAXN.
